comments: Robinson (MIA) and Matthews (LAL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Kuzma (LAL) turns into Butler's (MIA) body and delivers contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Nunn (MIA) moves his arm somewhat forward towards James' (LAL) path and he absorbs the marginal contact.
Robinson (MIA) moves into Kuzma (LAL) and makes body contact that affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Iguodala (MIA) is already in Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Adebayo (MIA) is already in Matthews' (LAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Butler (MIA) and Matthews (LAL) make incidental contact with one another as they come over the pick.
Matthews (LAL) is moving alongside Butler's (MIA) path and maintains a legal guarding position on the perimeter.
Butler (MIA) legally contests Kuzma's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Nunn (MIA) and Matthews (LAL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Robinson (MIA) is already in Matthews' (LAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Adebayo (MIA) is already in Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Gasol (LAL) is moving alongside Butler's (MIA) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket.
Robinson (MI)A initiates contact with his elbow and contact occurs to Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) head.
Matthews (LAL) is already in Iguodala's (MIA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
James (LAL) is already in Adebayo's (MIA) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Gasol (LAL) and Olynyk (MIA) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Olynyk (MIA) makes incidental body contact with Matthews (LAL) that occurs after Matthews has returned to the floor following his jump shot attempt.
Kuzma (LAL) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
James (LAL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Butler (MIA).
Butler (MIA) legally contests Caruso's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
